{"tha-ap329:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap329:0.2":"Umapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap329:0.3":"Niggundipupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap329:1.1":"“Yada devo devakaya, ","tha-ap329:1.2":"cavate ayusankhaya; ","tha-ap329:1.3":"Tayo sadda niccharanti, ","tha-ap329:1.4":"devanam anumodatam. ","tha-ap329:2.1":"‘Ito bho sugatim gaccha, ","tha-ap329:2.2":"manussanam sahabyatam; ","tha-ap329:2.3":"Manussabhuto saddhamme, ","tha-ap329:2.4":"labha saddham anuttaram. ","tha-ap329:3.1":"Sa te saddha nivitthassa, ","tha-ap329:3.2":"mulajata patitthita; ","tha-ap329:3.3":"Yavajivam asamhira, ","tha-ap329:3.4":"saddhamme suppavedite. ","tha-ap329:4.1":"Kayena kusalam katva, ","tha-ap329:4.2":"vacaya kusalam bahum; ","tha-ap329:4.3":"Manasa kusalam katva, ","tha-ap329:4.4":"abyapajjam nirupadhim. ","tha-ap329:5.1":"Tato opadhikam punnam, ","tha-ap329:5.2":"katva danena tam bahum; ","tha-ap329:5.3":"Annepi macce saddhamme, ","tha-ap329:5.4":"brahmacariye nivesaya’. ","tha-ap329:6.1":"Imaya anukampaya, ","tha-ap329:6.2":"devadevam yada vidu; ","tha-ap329:6.3":"Cavantam anumodanti, ","tha-ap329:6.4":"ehi deva punappunam. ","tha-ap329:7.1":"‘Samvego me tada asi, ","tha-ap329:7.2":"devasanghe samagate; ","tha-ap329:7.3":"Kamsu nama aham yonim, ","tha-ap329:7.4":"gamissami ito cuto’. ","tha-ap329:8.1":"Mama samvegamannaya, ","tha-ap329:8.2":"samano bhavitindriyo; ","tha-ap329:8.3":"Mamuddharitukamo so, ","tha-ap329:8.4":"agacchi mama santikam. ","tha-ap329:9.1":"Sumano nama namena, ","tha-ap329:9.2":"padumuttarasavako; ","tha-ap329:9.3":"Atthadhammanusasitva, ","tha-ap329:9.4":"samvejesi mamam tada. ","tha-ap329:10.1":"Dvadasamam bhanavaram. ","tha-ap329:11.1":"Tassaham vacanam sutva, ","tha-ap329:11.2":"buddhe cittam pasadayim; ","tha-ap329:11.3":"Tam dhiram abhivadetva, ","tha-ap329:11.4":"tattha kalankato aham. ","tha-ap329:12.1":"Upapajjim sa tattheva, ","tha-ap329:12.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap329:12.3":"Vasanto matukucchimhi, ","tha-ap329:12.4":"puna dhareti matuya. ","tha-ap329:13.1":"Tamha kaya cavitvana, ","tha-ap329:13.2":"tidase upapajjaham; ","tha-ap329:13.3":"Etthantare na passami, ","tha-ap329:13.4":"domanassamaham tada. ","tha-ap329:14.1":"Tavatimsa cavitvana, ","tha-ap329:14.2":"matukucchim samokkamim; ","tha-ap329:14.3":"Nikkhamitvana kucchimha, ","tha-ap329:14.4":"kanhasukkam ajanaham. ","tha-ap329:15.1":"Jatiya sattavassova, ","tha-ap329:15.2":"aramam pavisim aham; ","tha-ap329:15.3":"Gotamassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap329:15.4":"sakyaputtassa tadino. ","tha-ap329:16.1":"Vittharike pavacane, ","tha-ap329:16.2":"bahujannamhi sasane; ","tha-ap329:16.3":"Addasam sasanakare, ","tha-ap329:16.4":"bhikkhavo tattha satthuno. ","tha-ap329:17.1":"Savatthi nama nagaram, ","tha-ap329:17.2":"raja tatthasi kosalo; ","tha-ap329:17.3":"Rathena nagayuttena, ","tha-ap329:17.4":"upesi bodhimuttamam. ","tha-ap329:18.1":"Tassaham nagam disvana, ","tha-ap329:18.2":"pubbakammam anussarim; ","tha-ap329:18.3":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap329:18.4":"samayam agamasaham. ","tha-ap329:19.1":"Jatiya sattavassova, ","tha-ap329:19.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","tha-ap329:19.3":"Yo so buddham upatthasi, ","tha-ap329:19.4":"anando nama savako. ","tha-ap329:20.1":"Gatima dhitima ceva, ","tha-ap329:20.2":"satima ca bahussuto; ","tha-ap329:20.3":"Ranno cittam pasadento, ","tha-ap329:20.4":"niyyadesi mahajuti. ","tha-ap329:21.1":"Tassaham dhammam sutvana, ","tha-ap329:21.2":"pubbakammam anussarim; ","tha-ap329:21.3":"Tattheva thitako santo, ","tha-ap329:21.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap329:22.1":"Ekamsam civaram katva, ","tha-ap329:22.2":"sire katvana anjalim; ","tha-ap329:22.3":"Sambuddham abhivadetva, ","tha-ap329:22.4":"imam vacam udirayim. ","tha-ap329:23.1":"‘Padumuttarabuddhassa, ","tha-ap329:23.2":"dvipadindassa satthuno; ","tha-ap329:23.3":"Niggundipuppham paggayha, ","tha-ap329:23.4":"sihasane thapesaham. ","tha-ap329:24.1":"Tena kammena dvipadinda, ","tha-ap329:24.2":"lokajettha narasabha; ","tha-ap329:24.3":"Pattomhi acalam thanam, ","tha-ap329:24.4":"hitva jayaparajayam’. ","tha-ap329:25.1":"Pancavisasahassamhi, ","tha-ap329:25.2":"kappanam manujadhipa; ","tha-ap329:25.3":"Abbudanirabbudani, ","tha-ap329:25.4":"atthatthasimsu khattiya. ","tha-ap329:26.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap329:26.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap329:26.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap329:27.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma niggundipupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap329:28.1":"Niggundipupphiyattherassapadanam sattamam. "}